    <body>Select the <b class="Bold">Disable Console for Group</b> checkbox to disable the <MadCap:variable name="General.ProductName" /> disconnected console for the group. If this checkbox is cleared (enabled) for the group and the <a href="../../../../Organization Configuration/Organizations/Mobile Configuration.htm#OfflineEnabled" target="_blank" alt="Offline Enabled">Offline Enabled</a> option is selected in the Mobile Configuration dialog in Organization Configuration &gt; Organization Settings, the Mobile Access section is visible in the My Preferences page in <MadCap:variable name="General.ProductName" />. <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="General.Online">See also "Mobile Access' in <MadCap:xref href="../../../../UserGuide/Preferences/Preferences.htm" target="_blank" alt="Preferences [User Instructions]">Preferences [User Instructions]</MadCap:xref>.</MadCap:conditionalText></body>
</html>